# {{uncountable}} A strong, uncontrollable, unpleasant [[emotion]] caused by actual or perceived danger or threat.
#:''He was struck by '''fear''' on seeing the snake.''
# {{countable}} A [[phobia]], a sense of fear induced by something or someone.<!--not a self-referential definition: the word "fear" here is used in the previous sense-->
#:''Not everybody has the same '''fears'''.''
#:''I have a '''fear''' of [[ant]]s.''
